&lt;h2&gt;About Hexnode&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hexnode is a &lt;strong&gt;global leader in Unified Endpoint Management (UEM)&lt;/strong&gt;, trusted by over 100 countries and managing millions of devices worldwide. With a rapid pace of innovation, we have established ourselves as a dominant force across Apple, Windows, Android, macOS, Linux, and tvOS.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Hexnode?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hexnode is a rare combination of global scale, product excellence, and startup-level velocity. We operate in a mission-critical category—supporting organizations that rely on secure, reliable device management every single day. Joining Hexnode means stepping into a company in hyper-growth mode.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Presales Coordinator, you will support the team by managing complex bid processes, coordinating technical responses, and ensuring seamless day-to-day operations. This role is designed for a detail-oriented professional who can manage high-stakes documentation, allowing our sales leaders to focus on driving revenue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bid &amp;amp; Proposal Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead the backend operations for RFPs, RFIs, EOIs, and audits. You will manage the end-to-end submission process, ensuring all technical and commercial questions are answered accurately and submitted before deadlines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Content Synthesis:&lt;/strong&gt; Quickly craft custom presales responses by leveraging and evolving our vast library of technical artifacts. You will edit non-writer submissions to ensure a consistent, professional brand voice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Knowledge Base Evolution:&lt;/strong&gt; Continually update and refine response templates to reflect market trends and Hexnode’s emerging product capabilities. Post-submission, you will &quot;scrub&quot; proposals of client-specific identifiers to maintain an evergreen internal database.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coordination &amp;amp; Admin:&lt;/strong&gt; Organize high-priority meetings, manage bid record-keeping via SharePoint/Teams/Google Drive, and manage administrative duties such as sharing agendas and recording/distributing Minutes of Meetings (MoMs).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Presentation Support:&lt;/strong&gt; Play a supporting role in preparing and participating in presentation rounds on an as-needed basis to ensure the sales team is fully equipped for final-stage bids.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Required Experience &amp;amp; Expertise&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of proven experience in Presales Coordination, Technical Sales, or Bid Management within the SaaS industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience responding to International RFPs and competitive bids.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to learn, understand and articulate complex technical concepts quickly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in UEM/Cybersecurity is a significant plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional proposal writing and editing skills with a high degree of attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be comfortable working US timings from our Chennai office.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in a relevant technical or business field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hexnode is an Equal Opportunity Employer. We welcome and encourage candidates of all backgrounds, identities, and experiences to apply.&lt;/p&gt;

