&lt;p&gt;As a Process Associate in the Sales Operations team, you will manage the end-to-end lifecycle of sales transactions, ensuring that our international sales teams (US/UK) have the operational support needed to close deals efficiently while maintaining perfect data integrity and financial compliance.&lt;/p&gt;
