&lt;div&gt;Workflows, schemes, custom fields, permissions&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Issue types, automation rules, notification schemes&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Boards, dashboards, filters, project templates&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
