&lt;div&gt;Manage Jira post-migration enhancements and troubleshooting as needed.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Integrate Jira with other tools such as Confluence and marketplace apps.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
